**Notes on filling this out**:

- Keep the `description` in frontmatter informative — it's the only thing always in the system prompt. Test by asking: "given only the description, would I know when to use this?"
- The body is loaded only when the skill is triggered. You can be more verbose here.
- If the skill calls scripts, put them in this folder and reference them with relative paths.
- One skill, one purpose. If you find yourself writing "and also...", split into two skills.
